@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="text-center mt-5 mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="lead">Welcome to LEARN's Privacy Policy page. At LEARN, we are committed to safeguarding your personal information and respecting your privacy. Please review our policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>LEARN collects information to enhance your educational experience. This includes:</p>
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Personal Information:</strong> such as your name, email address, and contact details when you register on our platform.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Educational Data:</strong> such as course progress, quiz results, assignments, and feedback, used to support your learning.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Usage Data:</strong> details about your interactions with LEARN, including session times and accessed content, to help improve our platform.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>We use your information to personalize and improve your experience on LEARN. Your data is used to:</p>
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">Customize course content and recommendations based on your learning progress.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Provide insights and analytics to develop our educational materials further.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Send you important updates, reminders, and resources relevant to your courses.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>LEARN does not sell or share your data with third parties for advertising. However, we may share limited information with:</p>
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">Trusted partners who assist us in providing and enhancing platform functionality.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Educational institutions to verify educational records, where applicable.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Authorities as required by law to comply with legal obligations.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>LEARN prioritizes your data security by implementing strict measures to prevent unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure. Access to your information is limited to authorized personnel only.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data on LEARN. For assistance managing your information, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>6. Updates to this Policy</h2>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>LEARN may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We encourage you to check this page regularly to stay informed about any changes.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
        Thank you for choosing LEARN for your educational journey. If you have any concerns or questions, please reach out to us at our support center.
    </div>
</div>
